==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fugacity
<hw>Fu*gac"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L
<ets>fugacitas</ets>: cf. F. <ets>fugacit⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality of being fugacious; fugaclousness;
volatility; <as>as, <ex>fugacity</ex> of spirits</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Boyle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Uncertainty; instability.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fugacy</ent>⟦br⟧
